    "body": "Add diversified micro SAAS, IT, and AI services and implement a futuristic design overhaul to the Zion Tech Group app.\n\nThis includes a new dedicated Micro SAAS Services page, along with animated backgrounds, neon effects, glassmorphism, and improved responsiveness across the header, footer, home, and service pages.\n\n---\n<a href=\"https://cursor.com/background-agent?bcId=bc-ddf32890-f49d-43ae-a69b-bda81e0791cf\">\n  <picture>\n    <source media=\"(prefers-color-scheme: dark)\" srcset=\"https://cursor.com/open-in-cursor-dark.svg\">\n    <source media=\"(prefers-color-scheme: light)\" srcset=\"https://cursor.com/open-in-cursor-light.svg\">\n    <img alt=\"Open in Cursor\" src=\"https://cursor.com/open-in-cursor.svg\">\n  </picture>\n</a>\n<a href=\"https://cursor.com/agents?id=bc-ddf32890-f49d-43ae-a69b-bda81e0791cf\">\n  <picture>\n    <source media=\"(prefers-color-scheme: dark)\" srcset=\"https://cursor.com/open-in-web-dark.svg\">\n    <source media=\"(prefers-color-scheme: light)\" srcset=\"https://cursor.com/open-in-web-light.svg\">\n    <img alt=\"Open in Web\" src=\"https://cursor.com/open-in-web.svg\">\n  </picture>\n</a>\n\n",
