    "body": "Fix broken links, create missing pages/routes, update canonical URLs, and enhance site navigation to improve website functionality.\n\nThis PR addresses the user's request to perform a deep analysis of the website, fix all broken links, create missing content, and improve the site's header, footer, and sidebar. Key changes include:\n- Correcting numerous internal routes and adding placeholder components for previously missing pages (e.g., FAQ, Admin Disputes, Create Profile, various Dashboard and Enterprise routes).\n- Updating all canonical URLs and structured data references from `app.ziontechgroup.com` to `ziontechgroup.com`.\n- Enhancing the main navigation with new \"Services\", \"Blog\", and \"About\" links, along with their corresponding translation keys.\n- Resolving a build failure by removing conflicting Next.js-style `pages` directories from the Vite/React Router project.\n\n---\n<a href=\"https://cursor.com/background-agent?bcId=bc-ee9bd691-642a-4778-bc1a-c71483ee7a1a\">\n  <picture>\n    <source media=\"(prefers-color-scheme: dark)\" srcset=\"https://cursor.com/open-in-cursor-dark.svg\">\n    <source media=\"(prefers-color-scheme: light)\" srcset=\"https://cursor.com/open-in-cursor-light.svg\">\n    <img alt=\"Open in Cursor\" src=\"https://cursor.com/open-in-cursor.svg\">\n  </picture>\n</a>\n<a href=\"https://cursor.com/agents?id=bc-ee9bd691-642a-4778-bc1a-c71483ee7a1a\">\n  <picture>\n    <source media=\"(prefers-color-scheme: dark)\" srcset=\"https://cursor.com/open-in-web-dark.svg\">\n    <source media=\"(prefers-color-scheme: light)\" srcset=\"https://cursor.com/open-in-web-light.svg\">\n    <img alt=\"Open in Web\" src=\"https://cursor.com/open-in-web.svg\">\n  </picture>\n</a>\n\n",
