    "body": "Implement new micro SAAS services and a comprehensive futuristic design overhaul to enhance the Zion Tech Group app.\n\nThis PR addresses the user's request for adding diversified AI, IT, and business micro SAAS services, alongside a complete redesign of the application. The changes include integrating new service data, creating a dedicated services page, enhancing the header and footer for improved navigation and contact information, and applying futuristic design elements, animations, and responsiveness across the entire site. Technical improvements, including fixing build errors and updating dependencies, were also performed.\n\n---\n<a href=\"https://cursor.com/background-agent?bcId=bc-33097267-a2d1-4c04-8936-dd2e43dee6fa\">\n  <picture>\n    <source media=\"(prefers-color-scheme: dark)\" srcset=\"https://cursor.com/open-in-cursor-dark.svg\">\n    <source media=\"(prefers-color-scheme: light)\" srcset=\"https://cursor.com/open-in-cursor-light.svg\">\n    <img alt=\"Open in Cursor\" src=\"https://cursor.com/open-in-cursor.svg\">\n  </picture>\n</a>\n<a href=\"https://cursor.com/agents?id=bc-33097267-a2d1-4c04-8936-dd2e43dee6fa\">\n  <picture>\n    <source media=\"(prefers-color-scheme: dark)\" srcset=\"https://cursor.com/open-in-web-dark.svg\">\n    <source media=\"(prefers-color-scheme: light)\" srcset=\"https://cursor.com/open-in-web-light.svg\">\n    <img alt=\"Open in Web\" src=\"https://cursor.com/open-in-web.svg\">\n  </picture>\n</a>\n\n",
