    "body": "Fix broken links, create missing pages, and improve site header/footer navigation to enhance the Zion Tech Group website's completeness and user experience.\n\nThe website had numerous broken links and referenced non-existent pages in its navigation and footer. This PR resolves these by creating essential missing pages (e.g., Mission, Team, News, Case Studies, legal pages) and reorganizing the main navigation and footer links for clarity. It also includes a fix for a build error caused by a conflicting Next.js file in the Vite/React project.\n\n---\n<a href=\"https://cursor.com/background-agent?bcId=bc-6c60576a-c693-4fd2-8ee8-84f5191bd37f\">\n  <picture>\n    <source media=\"(prefers-color-scheme: dark)\" srcset=\"https://cursor.com/open-in-cursor-dark.svg\">\n    <source media=\"(prefers-color-scheme: light)\" srcset=\"https://cursor.com/open-in-cursor-light.svg\">\n    <img alt=\"Open in Cursor\" src=\"https://cursor.com/open-in-cursor.svg\">\n  </picture>\n</a>\n<a href=\"https://cursor.com/agents?id=bc-6c60576a-c693-4fd2-8ee8-84f5191bd37f\">\n  <picture>\n    <source media=\"(prefers-color-scheme: dark)\" srcset=\"https://cursor.com/open-in-web-dark.svg\">\n    <source media=\"(prefers-color-scheme: light)\" srcset=\"https://cursor.com/open-in-web-light.svg\">\n    <img alt=\"Open in Web\" src=\"https://cursor.com/open-in-web.svg\">\n  </picture>\n</a>\n\n",
