    "body": "Expand ZionTechGroup's service offerings with new micro SAAS, IT, and AI solutions, and refresh the website with a futuristic design and improved responsiveness.\n\nThis includes a comprehensive update to the header, footer, and navigation, the introduction of futuristic visual effects like glass morphism and neon, and resolution of all build-time TypeScript errors.\n\n---\n<a href=\"https://cursor.com/background-agent?bcId=bc-a911ced3-06f5-4cc2-8e66-26d88333a9ac\">\n  <picture>\n    <source media=\"(prefers-color-scheme: dark)\" srcset=\"https://cursor.com/open-in-cursor-dark.svg\">\n    <source media=\"(prefers-color-scheme: light)\" srcset=\"https://cursor.com/open-in-cursor-light.svg\">\n    <img alt=\"Open in Cursor\" src=\"https://cursor.com/open-in-cursor.svg\">\n  </picture>\n</a>\n<a href=\"https://cursor.com/agents?id=bc-a911ced3-06f5-4cc2-8e66-26d88333a9ac\">\n  <picture>\n    <source media=\"(prefers-color-scheme: dark)\" srcset=\"https://cursor.com/open-in-web-dark.svg\">\n    <source media=\"(prefers-color-scheme: light)\" srcset=\"https://cursor.com/open-in-web-light.svg\">\n    <img alt=\"Open in Web\" src=\"https://cursor.com/open-in-web.svg\">\n  </picture>\n</a>\n\n",
