    "body": "Adds diversified micro SAAS, IT, and AI services and implements a futuristic design overhaul with enhanced navigation and responsiveness.\n\nThis PR addresses the client's request to expand service offerings with detailed pricing, and to significantly improve the app's aesthetic and usability through a futuristic design, animated backgrounds, neon effects, and a more organized navigation structure. It also includes critical build fixes.\n\n---\n<a href=\"https://cursor.com/background-agent?bcId=bc-9d5d7d4c-3a98-4159-ab92-360cb8673981\">\n  <picture>\n    <source media=\"(prefers-color-scheme: dark)\" srcset=\"https://cursor.com/open-in-cursor-dark.svg\">\n    <source media=\"(prefers-color-scheme: light)\" srcset=\"https://cursor.com/open-in-cursor-light.svg\">\n    <img alt=\"Open in Cursor\" src=\"https://cursor.com/open-in-cursor.svg\">\n  </picture>\n</a>\n<a href=\"https://cursor.com/agents?id=bc-9d5d7d4c-3a98-4159-ab92-360cb8673981\">\n  <picture>\n    <source media=\"(prefers-color-scheme: dark)\" srcset=\"https://cursor.com/open-in-web-dark.svg\">\n    <source media=\"(prefers-color-scheme: light)\" srcset=\"https://cursor.com/open-in-web-light.svg\">\n    <img alt=\"Open in Web\" src=\"https://cursor.com/open-in-web.svg\">\n  </picture>\n</a>\n\n",
