    "body": "Add diversified micro SAAS, IT, and AI services with detailed advertising and correct contact information to expand the platform's offerings.\n\nThe implementation involved creating new service pages (`ComprehensiveServices`, `AIServicesPage`, `EnterpriseSolutions`), integrating them into the application's routing and navigation, and updating the footer with the correct contact details. Several build and merge conflicts were resolved, including fixing incorrect icon imports and a Next.js specific error component in a React/Vite project, to ensure a successful and clean deployment.\n\n---\n<a href=\"https://cursor.com/background-agent?bcId=bc-407c437c-20f4-4b52-8d84-362ff70daed0\">\n  <picture>\n    <source media=\"(prefers-color-scheme: dark)\" srcset=\"https://cursor.com/open-in-cursor-dark.svg\">\n    <source media=\"(prefers-color-scheme: light)\" srcset=\"https://cursor.com/open-in-cursor-light.svg\">\n    <img alt=\"Open in Cursor\" src=\"https://cursor.com/open-in-cursor.svg\">\n  </picture>\n</a>\n<a href=\"https://cursor.com/agents?id=bc-407c437c-20f4-4b52-8d84-362ff70daed0\">\n  <picture>\n    <source media=\"(prefers-color-scheme: dark)\" srcset=\"https://cursor.com/open-in-web-dark.svg\">\n    <source media=\"(prefers-color-scheme: light)\" srcset=\"https://cursor.com/open-in-web-light.svg\">\n    <img alt=\"Open in Web\" src=\"https://cursor.com/open-in-web.svg\">\n  </picture>\n</a>\n\n",
