    "body": "Add new AI, Cybersecurity, Cloud, and Data Analytics services and update site navigation to diversify ZionTech Group's offerings.\n\nThis PR introduces four new dedicated service pages with detailed descriptions, features, benefits, and pricing. It also updates the main `ServicesPage` and `CategoriesSection` to integrate these new offerings. Several build and TypeScript errors were resolved during implementation, including adapting a Next.js-specific error component to the current Vite/React environment, ensuring all changes are functional and the application builds successfully.\n\n---\n<a href=\"https://cursor.com/background-agent?bcId=bc-f7c1b600-c78b-418b-a9b8-27da347d0412\">\n  <picture>\n    <source media=\"(prefers-color-scheme: dark)\" srcset=\"https://cursor.com/open-in-cursor-dark.svg\">\n    <source media=\"(prefers-color-scheme: light)\" srcset=\"https://cursor.com/open-in-cursor-light.svg\">\n    <img alt=\"Open in Cursor\" src=\"https://cursor.com/open-in-cursor.svg\">\n  </picture>\n</a>\n<a href=\"https://cursor.com/agents?id=bc-f7c1b600-c78b-418b-a9b8-27da347d0412\">\n  <picture>\n    <source media=\"(prefers-color-scheme: dark)\" srcset=\"https://cursor.com/open-in-web-dark.svg\">\n    <source media=\"(prefers-color-scheme: light)\" srcset=\"https://cursor.com/open-in-web-light.svg\">\n    <img alt=\"Open in Web\" src=\"https://cursor.com/open-in-web.svg\">\n  </picture>\n</a>\n\n",
