    "body": "Add diversified micro SAAS services and implement a futuristic design overhaul to enhance user experience and service offerings.\n\nThis PR introduces new AI, IT, and Development & Automation micro SAAS services with detailed features and pricing. The application's design has been transformed with futuristic elements like neon effects, animated backgrounds, and improved navigation, alongside technical fixes for responsiveness and TypeScript issues, to provide a modern and engaging user interface.\n\n---\n<a href=\"https://cursor.com/background-agent?bcId=bc-81b118d0-2159-4336-aa8b-dda15d370bf7\">\n  <picture>\n    <source media=\"(prefers-color-scheme: dark)\" srcset=\"https://cursor.com/open-in-cursor-dark.svg\">\n    <source media=\"(prefers-color-scheme: light)\" srcset=\"https://cursor.com/open-in-cursor-light.svg\">\n    <img alt=\"Open in Cursor\" src=\"https://cursor.com/open-in-cursor.svg\">\n  </picture>\n</a>\n<a href=\"https://cursor.com/agents?id=bc-81b118d0-2159-4336-aa8b-dda15d370bf7\">\n  <picture>\n    <source media=\"(prefers-color-scheme: dark)\" srcset=\"https://cursor.com/open-in-web-dark.svg\">\n    <source media=\"(prefers-color-scheme: light)\" srcset=\"https://cursor.com/open-in-web-light.svg\">\n    <img alt=\"Open in Web\" src=\"https://cursor.com/open-in-web.svg\">\n  </picture>\n</a>\n\n",
